A software package implementing the regression method for estimating 
performance in a rapid serial visual presentation target detection task of 
Files & Marathe (2016).

If you use this code for any publication, please cite the following paper:

Files, B. T., & Marathe, A. R. (2016). A regression method for estimating 
    performance in a rapid serial visual presentation target detection 
    task. Journal of Neuroscience Methods, 258, 114-123. 
    http://doi.org/10.1016/j.jneumeth.2015.11.003


